The paper discusses modifications to temporal difference (TD) methods in hierarchical reinforcement learning (HRL) systems, which are commonly used in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY), which are related to HRL. Finally, the paper discusses policy improvement (cs.MA), which is a common topic in reinforcement learning.
